    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#mohamed-jmr1997"/>, pp. 34-35 n. <citedRange>4 D</citedRange> (ph.)</bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>47.2180, D</citedRange></bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>086500</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            <p>Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#belzic2022"/>, catalogue <citedRange>B.43</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Κριν_"><seg part="I">Κρι<unclear>ν</unclear><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="medium"/></seg></name>
                    <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested" key=""><name nymRef="#Ἀρίστιππος" type="patronymic">Ἀρισ<unclear>τίπ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">πω</supplied></name></persName></persName>
                </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p>
                    <app loc="1">
                        <rdg resp="#mohamed-jmr1997">Κρῖν<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ις</supplied></rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <app loc="2">
                        <rdg resp="#mohamed-jmr1997">Ἀρισ<unclear>τίπ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">που</supplied></rdg>
                    </app>
               </p>
 </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Krin<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fils (ou fille ?) d'Aristippos.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Krin<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> son (or daughter?) of Aristippos.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Krin<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> figlio (o figlia?) di Aristippos.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The first editors, on the view that the base comes from the same tomb as <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr08100</ref> and <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr086400</ref>, tried to find names common to those epitaphs 
                    and retained <foreign xml:lang="grc">Κρῖνις</foreign> as a possible restoration. However, the provenance might not be very clear. Moreover, the careful lettering shows a somewhat earlier date for the present 
                    inscription; the spacing of the letters and the place of the hole on top show that the gap was of ca. 5 letters at l. 1.</p>
            </div></body>
    </text>
